        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(13 comments)\n\nCreation of the Drools election handler and standby state handler was done over many months and 3 developers.  Consequently, there are a number of bits and pieces left behind which are artifacts of the development.  I have done the following cleanup:\n - Removed dead/unused code\n - Removed commented code\n - Removed all println and stacktrace executions\n - Logged all exceptions\n\n - Kevin",
